Anxiety disorders are feedback loops.

Fear causes anxiety/symptoms. We learn to fear this, causing more symptoms. The sensitized body becomes hyperaware of everything we feel/think which causes fear.

The ONLY way to reduce symptoms is to be comfortable with them.
